---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us" navbar={true}>
  <div class="title">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="about-us">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="image-content left">
        <img src="https://placehold.co/400" alt="Placeholder Image 1">
      </div>
      <div class="text-content right">
        <h2>Who Are We?</h2>
        <p>
          CMK is a leading provider of customized computer peripherals, dedicated
          to enhancing your computing experience. Our team of experts is passionate
          about technology and design, ensuring that every product we create meets
          the highest standards of quality and performance.
        </p>
        <p>
          We understand that every user has unique needs and preferences. That's
          why we offer a wide range of customizable options for our keyboards and
          mice, allowing you to create the perfect setup for your style and
          performance requirements. Whether you're a gamer, designer, or professional,
          we've got you covered.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="text-content left">
        <p>
          Welcome to CMK, your go-to destination for premium customized computer
          peripherals. We specialize in tailoring keyboards and mice to suit your
          style, performance needs, and comfort. Whether you are a gamer, designer,
          or office professional, we provide high-quality, durable, and
          aesthetically crafted products to enhance your experience.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          At CMK, our mission is to revolutionize the way you interact with your
          computer. We believe that every individual has unique preferences, and our
          goal is to offer custom solutions that elevate comfort, efficiency, and
          performance. We aim to empower gamers, creatives, and professionals by
          providing high-quality peripherals that are designed for excellence.
        </p>

        <h2>What We Offer</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Fully customizable mechanical keyboards with switch and keycap options</li>
          <li>Personalized gaming mice with ergonomic enhancements</li>
          <li>RGB lighting and software customization for an immersive experience</li>
          <li>Premium materials ensuring durability and longevity</li>
          <li>Exclusive limited-edition designs and collaborations</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="image-content right">
        <img src="https://placehold.co/400" alt="Placeholder Image 2">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="image-content left">
        <img src="https://placehold.co/400" alt="Placeholder Image 3">
      </div>
      <div class="text-content right">
        <p>
          Our commitment to quality sets us apart. Every product we create undergoes
          rigorous testing to ensure superior performance and longevity. We use only
          the finest materials to deliver peripherals that offer both style and
          function.
        </p>
        <p>
          Customer satisfaction is our top priority. Our team of experts is always
          ready to assist you with personalized recommendations and support,
          ensuring a seamless customization experience.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="text-content left">
        <h2>Join the CMK Community</h2>
        <p>
          Beyond just products, CMK is a growing community of tech enthusiasts who
          share a passion for innovation and customization. Join us on our journey
          by following us on social media, participating in our exclusive events,
          and staying updated on our latest designs.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="image-content right">
        <img src="https://placehold.co/400" alt="Placeholder Image 4">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-container last">
      <div class="image-content left">
        <img src="https://placehold.co/400" alt="Placeholder Image 5">
      </div>
      <div class="text-content right">
        <h2>Want to give us a hand?</h2>
        <p>
          We're always looking for new ideas and ways to improve our products. If
          you have a creative idea or a unique feature request, please don't hesitate
          to reach out to us. Your input is invaluable in shaping the future of CMK.
        </p>
        <p>
          We're also open to collaborations and partnerships. If you're interested in
          working together, please reach out to us. Together, we can create innovative
          solutions that push the boundaries of what's possible.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <button>Get in Touch</button>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
   .image-content img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .title {
    margin-top: 10rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .title h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #f9eeee;
  }

  .about-us {
    padding: 20px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-container {
    display: flex;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: stretch; /* Make items the same height */
  }

  .image-content {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
  }

  .text-content {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .image-content img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .left {
    order: -1; /* Image on the left */
  }

  .right {
    order: 1; /* Text on the right */
  }

  .text-content h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #f4f4f4;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .text-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #e7dcdc;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .text-content ul {
    list-style-type: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .text-content ul li {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem; /* Space for bullet/icon */
  }

  .text-content ul li::before {
    content: 'â€¢'; /* You can replace this with a checkmark or other icon */
    color: #27ae60;
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.2rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .last {
    margin-bottom: 6rem; /* Add some extra space at the end */
  }

  .last .text-content {
    align-items: center;
    text-align: right; /* Align text to the right in the last section */
  }

  .last .image-content {
    order: -1; /* Image on the left in the last section */
  }

  .last h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #f4f4f4;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .last p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #e7dcdc;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .last a {
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .last button {
    background-color: transparent;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
    border: 2px solid #27ae60;
    border-radius: 5px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .last button:hover {
    background-color: #27ae60;
  }

  /* Responsive adjustments */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-container {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .image-content {
      order: 0; /* Reset order on smaller screens */
    }

    .text-content {
      order: 0; /* Reset order on smaller screens */
      padding: 15px;
    }

    .text-content.right {
      order: 0; /* Ensure text is below image */
    }

    .text-content.left {
      order: 0; /* Ensure text is below image */
    }

    .text-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .text-content p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .last .text-content {
      text-align: center; /* Center text on smaller screens */
    }
  }
</style>